OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784641699
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to promise UK 'breathing
OL,4,Croom' on cost of living as he becomes
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FAndy Burnham will become prime
OL,8,Fminister on Monday, replacing Sir Keir
OL,9,FStarmer and pledging to give
OL,10,Fstruggling households some "breathing
OL,11,Froom" on the rising cost of living.
OL,13,FIn his first speech as prime minister,
OL,14,FBurnham is expected to urge the
OL,15,Fcountry to be honest about the
OL,16,Fchallenges it faces and call for
OL,17,F"reflection and resolution".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784641699
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to promise UK 'breathing
OL,4,Croom' on cost of living as he becomes
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FStarmer will deliver his final address
OL,8,Fas prime minister on Monday morning,
OL,9,Fbefore he and Burnham visit King
OL,10,FCharles in Buckingham Palace.
OL,12,FAgainst the backdrop of the UK having
OL,13,Fhad seven prime ministers over the
OL,14,Fpast decade, Burnham will warn he is
OL,15,F"acutely conscious" of the need for
OL,16,Fmore stable and responsible politics,
OL,17,Fpledging to restore faith in
OL,18,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784641699
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to promise UK 'breathing
OL,4,Croom' on cost of living as he becomes
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FBefore the speech, Starmer is expected
OL,8,Fto make his own address outside No 10
OL,9,Fbefore heading to Buckingham Palace to
OL,10,Fformally resign before Burnham meets
OL,11,Fthe King to "kiss hands" and be
OL,12,Fappointed prime minister.
OL,14,FUnlike Starmer's statement announcing
OL,15,Fhis resignation, neither speech is
OL,16,Flikely to be interrupted by protesters
OL,17,Fafter the police banned amplified
OL,18,Fmusic outside Downing Street during
OL,19,Fthe handover.
OL,26,@sD@MOUsD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784641699
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to promise UK 'breathing
OL,4,Croom' on cost of living as he becomes
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FAfter his speech, Burnham is expected
OL,8,Fto name his cabinet.
OL,10,FHe has been tight-lipped about his
OL,11,Fselections, but is believed to have
OL,12,Fbeen weighing up either Energy
OL,13,FSecretary Ed Miliband or Home
OL,14,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood to be
OL,15,Fchancellor.
OL,17,FMonday caps a rapid transition for
OL,18,FBurnham, coming barely a month after
OL,19,Fhe returned to Westminster following
OL,20,Fhis victory in the Makerfield by-
OL,21,Felection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784641699
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to promise UK 'breathing
OL,4,Croom' on cost of living as he becomes
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FWithout a full leadership contest, the
OL,8,Fnew prime minister is also yet to set
OL,9,Fout much of his agenda for his
OL,10,Fpremiership.
OL,12,FHe has said he wants to devolve power
OL,13,Faway from Westminster as one of his
OL,14,Fkey priorities, driving that agenda
OL,15,Fwith a new "No 10 North" in
OL,16,FManchester, which he is expected to
OL,17,Fvisit later in the week.
OL,26,@wD@LOUwD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
