CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784641699
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to promise UK 'breathing
OL,4,Croom' on cost of living as he becomes
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FPromising a "reset of priorities",
OL,8,FBurnham has also announced he will
OL,9,Fscrap Starmer's flagship digital ID
OL,10,Fprogramme to focus money and attention
OL,11,Fon the cost of living.
OL,13,FIn his first week in office, the new
OL,14,Fprime minister is expected to unveil
OL,15,Fpolicies aimed at making people's
OL,16,Flives easier.
OL,18,FReports have suggested this could
OL,19,Finclude action on energy bills,
OL,20,Fincluding allowing more oil and gas
OL,21,Fdrilling in the North Sea.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784641699
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to promise UK 'breathing
OL,4,Croom' on cost of living as he becomes
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FEnvironmental campaigners have urged
OL,8,Fhim to stick to Labour's 2024
OL,9,Fmanifesto, which promised not to issue
OL,10,Fnew licences for North Sea drilling,
OL,11,Farguing that they would not reduce
OL,12,Fenergy bills.
OL,14,FWriting on his Truth Social platform,
OL,15,FUS President Donald Trump pounced upon
OL,16,Fthese reports with glee, claiming that
OL,17,Fthe people of Aberdeen will be
OL,18,F"dancing in the streets".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
