PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784641699
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to promise UK 'breathing
OL,4,Croom' on cost of living as he becomes
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FDespite Burnham not confirming
OL,8,Fanything of the sort, Trump claimed
OL,9,Fthat "Andy Burnham, has stated that he
OL,10,Fwill be opening up, all the way, the
OL,11,Finvaluable North Sea Oil!".
OL,13,FHe said that this would "make the
OL,14,FUnited Kingdom, from a Poverty
OL,15,FStricken Disaster, to one of the
OL,16,FRichest Countries anywhere in the
OL,17,FWorld".
OL,26,@sD@ZO]uD@YOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
