OL,3,CAndy Burnham to promise UK 'breathing
OL,4,Croom' on cost of living as he becomes
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FBurnham could also face a decision on
OL,8,Fwhether to temporarily nationalise
OL,9,FThames Water as the firm struggles
OL,10,Fwith a #20 billion debt pile.
OL,12,FHe has already expressed support for
OL,13,Fgreater public control of essential
OL,14,Fservices, and Thames Water's main
OL,15,Fcreditors have said they are willing
OL,16,Fto discuss the issue with his new
OL,17,Fministers in an effort to agree a
OL,18,Frescue deal and avoid the business
OL,19,Ffalling into a so-called "special
OL,20,Fadministration regime".
OL,26,@{D@ZOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
