OL,3,CAndy Burnham to promise UK 'breathing
OL,4,Croom' on cost of living as he becomes
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FAnother priority is likely to be
OL,8,Freforming social care, which he has
OL,9,Fsaid is something he wishes to "expend
OL,10,Fpolitical capital" on.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
