PN,31711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784641699
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to promise UK 'breathing
OL,4,Croom' on cost of living as he becomes
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FLiberal Democrat leader Sir Ed Davey
OL,8,Fhas urged Burnham to engage other
OL,9,Fparties to solve the "social care
OL,10,Fcrisis", calling for guaranteed rights
OL,11,Ffor family carers, a universal safety
OL,12,Fnet and protection against
OL,13,F"catastrophic costs".
OL,15,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch has
OL,16,Falso written to Burnham, saying her
OL,17,Fparty will work with him to cut the
OL,18,Fwelfare bill and calling for him to
OL,19,Frule out tax rises and back new oil
OL,20,Fand gas drilling.
OL,26,@qD@VOUrD@GO]uD@AOUuD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
