CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784641699
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to promise UK 'breathing
OL,4,Croom' on cost of living as he becomes
OL,5,CPM
OL,7,FBadenoch told Burnham she would "never
OL,8,Fshirk" from holding him to account,
OL,9,Fadding: "You will enter office without
OL,10,Fhaving set out a clear plan on any of
OL,11,Fthe issues facing our country.
OL,13,F"You have refused calls to come to
OL,14,FParliament for questions from MPs, and
OL,15,Fyou have not submitted yourself to
OL,16,Fserious media scrutiny. This is not a
OL,17,Fpromising start."
OL,26,@oD@aOUpD@FO]qD@IOUuD@AOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
